trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" /> objects in a document-level customization that was created by using the Office development tools in Visual Studio.
trans-unit.target: 表示文档级自定义中 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" /> 对象的集合，该文档级自定义通过使用 Visual Studio 中的 Office 开发工具创建。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItem.CachedData%2A> property to obtain a <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItemCollection> for an Office solution document that has cached data.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItem.CachedData%2A>属性来获取<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItemCollection>为 Office 解决方案文档，已缓存数据。

trans-unit.source: For more information about caching data in document-level customizations, see [Caching Data](/visualstudio/vsto/caching-data.md) and [Accessing Data in Documents on the Server](/visualstudio/vsto/accessing-data-in-documents-on-the-server.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关在文档级自定义项中缓存数据的详细信息，请参阅[缓存数据](/visualstudio/vsto/caching-data.md)和[访问的服务器上的文档数据](/visualstudio/vsto/accessing-data-in-documents-on-the-server.md)。

trans-unit.source: The name of the object to add to the data cache.
trans-unit.target: 要添加到数据缓存的对象的名称。

trans-unit.source: The full assembly-qualified name of the type of the object to add to the data cache.
trans-unit.target: 要添加到数据缓存的对象类型的完整程序集限定名称。

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" /> to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 将指定的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" /> 添加到集合末尾。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" /> that was added to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 被添加到集合末尾的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" />。

trans-unit.source: For details about the format of an assembly-qualified name of a type, see the <xref:System.Type.AssemblyQualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: 类型的程序集限定名的格式的详细信息，请参阅<xref:System.Type.AssemblyQualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>属性。

trans-unit.source: To add a <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem> to the collection at a specific index location, use the <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection%601.Insert%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要添加<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem>到集合中的特定索引位置处，使用<xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection%601.Insert%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" /> that corresponds to <paramref name="dataId" /> already exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 此集合中已存在对应于 <paramref name="dataId" /> 的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" />。

trans-unit.source: The name of the cached data object.
trans-unit.target: 缓存的数据对象的名称。

trans-unit.source: Returns a value that indicates whether the collection contains the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" />.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个指示集合是否包含指定的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" /> 的值。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the collection contains a <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" /> that corresponds to the <paramref name="dataId" /> parameter; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果集合包含对应于 <paramref name="dataId" /> 参数的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" />，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItemEnumerator" /> that can be used to iterate through the contents of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个可用于循环访问集合内容的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItemEnumerator" />。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItemEnumerator" /> that can be used to iterate through the contents of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 可用于循环访问集合内容的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItemEnumerator" />。

trans-unit.source: The name of the cached data object.
trans-unit.target: 缓存的数据对象的名称。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" /> identified by the name of the cached data object.
trans-unit.target: 获取由缓存的数据对象的名称标识的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" /> that corresponds to the <paramref name="dataID" /> parameter; <see langword="null" /> if no <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" /> that corresponds to <paramref name="dataID" /> was found.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" />相对应的<paramref name="dataID" />参数;<see langword="null" />如果没有<see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" />相对应的<paramref name="dataID" />找到。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem> provides access to a cached data object in a document-level customization.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem>提供对中的文档级自定义项的缓存的数据对象的访问。

trans-unit.source: The name of the cached data object.
trans-unit.target: 缓存的数据对象的名称。

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" />, identified by the name of the cached data object, from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 从集合中删除由缓存数据对象的名称标识的指定 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem" />。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem> provides access to a cached data object in a document-level customization.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItem>提供对中的文档级自定义项的缓存的数据对象的访问。
